# Bible Webhook for Dialogflow ES

## Setup

1. Install dependencies:
   npm install

2. Start the server locally:
   npm start

3. (Optional) Expose locally using ngrok:
   ngrok http 3000

4. In Dialogflow ES:
   - Go to Fulfillment → Enable Webhook → Paste your HTTPS URL
   - Enable “Webhook call for this intent” in your ReadBibleVerse intent.

5. Test in Dialogflow:
   User: John 3:16
   Bot: John 3:16 — For God so loved the world...
